{"tid":795662,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬些路承認：掛住C朗","createTime":"2018-08-27T07:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T07:57:59.000Z","uid":153600,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fc7985e0e18614e3148e58014012c04b149b01","tid":795662,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=aMUKI9mitcimM%2Bg9U%2B1JdDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1fcde186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】就算皇家馬德里於西甲開季2戰全勝，但左閘馬些路仍表示，記掛著今夏離隊的基斯坦奴朗拿度。<br />\n<br />\n「基斯坦奴朗拿度仍然是世界上最佳球員，我當然想念他。」馬些路（Marcelo）說。「不過，加里夫巴利、賓施馬同樣非常出色。<br />\n<br />\n周日西甲，巴利、賓施馬合共轟入3個入球，帶領皇家馬德里以4:1大勝主場的基羅納；當中巴利更攻入近5場比賽第4球，而賓施馬今戰亦梅開二度。<br />\n<br />\n馬些路甚少被換出，但今戰踢了約1小時就被中堅華拉尼入替，他表示：「我很意外，但尊重教練的決定。我希望繼續踢，因為感覺自己有百分百狀態，但球隊正處於正軌，肯定每場都會進步。」<br />\n<br />\n對於新加盟門將泰拔高圖爾斯未有上陣機會，上仗仍然由基羅拿華斯把關，馬些路也力撐後者：「我們有2名非常出色的門將，我為基羅感到高興，他一直都踢得很好。」"},{"pid":"608aa0c98efe1ccfb591fc5d186abb5e54e31f78","tid":795662,"uid":17945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">this</span>"},{"pid":"672b96d83aa4d24313793bf24051100ca65d8cb8","tid":795662,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"608aa0c98efe1ccfb591fc5d186abb5e54e31f78","tid":795662,"uid":17945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">this</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"is"},{"pid":"1f86923855c194f0b1c1a259672702cbc9403089","tid":795662,"uid":155197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"672b96d83aa4d24313793bf24051100ca65d8cb8","tid":795662,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"608aa0c98efe1ccfb591fc5d186abb5e54e31f78","tid":795662,"uid":17945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">this</span>"},"citedBy